Package org.svvrl.goal.core.tran.extendedonthefly

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExtendedOnTheFly
    This class provides an interface for the settings of an on-the-fly algorithm.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cover
    This class provides methods for computing the cover for the on-the-fly algorithms GPVW, GPVW+, and LTL2AUT.
    CoverWithPrimeImplicant
    This class provides a method for computing the cover of a set of LTL formulae with prime implicants.
